dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents zoning for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2015. [This file contains the polygons for all parcels in Jefferson County and the data related to the zone of the parcel.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This file contains the zoning polygons for all parcels in Jefferson County. The data is complete for all the Towns. We are in the process of collecting data for all Cities and Villages and adding that data to this file. As of Oct. 2010, we had data for the Cities of Watertown, Fort Atkinson, Lake Mills & Waterloo and for the Villages of Johnson Creek and Palmyra.]
